==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: jewels-of-opar
<hw>jewels-of-opar</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An erect plant (<spn>Talinum
paniculatum</spn>) with tuberous roots and terminal panicles of red to
yellow flowers, growing from Southwestern North America to Central
America; it has been widely introduced elsewhere.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> <spn>Talinum paniculatum</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jewelweed</ent>⟦br⟧
